00:00:16.780 --> 00:00:19.680
And what a blessing that is.

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:22.319
If you have your Bible with you this evening, Psalm 23,

00:00:22.319 --> 00:00:25.520
and a couple of weeks ago, we started looking

00:00:25.520 --> 00:00:27.360
at Jehovah Ra, the Lord, my shepherd.

00:00:27.559 --> 00:00:32.159
And so we'll be continuing, I mentioned to you

00:00:32.159 --> 00:00:34.060
when we arrived to the name Jehovah Ra,

00:00:34.060 --> 00:00:36.099
