and some of them, for periods of time,

00:11:32.380 --> 00:11:34.340
just, they were impenetrable.

00:11:34.340 --> 00:11:36.060
I mean, there was nothing that an enemy could do.

00:11:36.060 --> 00:11:38.660
It was amazing where they would build them

00:11:38.660 --> 00:11:40.700
and all that they had.

00:11:40.700 --> 00:11:44.580
And David says, God is my rock and he's my fortress.

00:11:44.580 --> 00:11:48.600
He's providing me with that security, that protection.

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:53.060
We find in Psalm 4.8,

00:11:53.060 --> 00:11:55.900
I know it's some chapters back,

00:11:55.900 --> 00:11:58.020
but look at Psalm 4.8, if you will,

