00:12:11.220 --> 00:12:14.199
I will both lay me down in peace and sleep,

00:12:15.139 --> 00:12:20.139
for thou, Lord, only makest me dwell in safety.

00:12:20.619 --> 00:12:22.460
Isn't that a good verse of scripture?

00:12:23.740 --> 00:12:25.900
It's a good verse of scripture.

00:12:25.900 --> 00:12:28.460
I understand we have security systems

00:12:28.460 --> 00:12:29.820
in the era in which we live

00:12:29.820 --> 00:12:33.600
and we have people that have various aspects of weaponry

