and so on and so forth, and I understand all of that.

00:12:36.820 --> 00:12:39.820
But can I tell you that there's no safety like God's safety?

00:12:41.100 --> 00:12:43.460
There's no safety like God's safety.

00:12:43.460 --> 00:12:46.940
The Bible says, the Proverbs 21 and verse 31,

00:12:46.940 --> 00:12:48.600
the Bible says that the horse is prepared

